
<h1>stream bouncer</h1>

<a class="ajax" href="/logout">Logout</a>

<h1>Past Bounces</h1>
<p>This is where we'll put a list of the three most recently expired bounces, if the user has any.</p>

<h1>Followers</h1>

<form class="ajax" action="/search">
	<input name="q" type="text" />
	<input type="reset" value="Clear" />
</form>

<ul id="search">
	<Everyone sorted by last time they were bounced

	<% 
		@logged_in_user.follows.each { |follow|
			twitter_user = follow.twitter_user 
	%>
		<li>
			<img src="<%= twitter_user.picture_url %>" />
			<div class="username"><%= twitter_user.username %></div>
			<div class="name"><%= twitter_user.name %></div>
			<% if follow.bounce.nil? %>
				<a class="ajax" href="/bounce">Bounce</a>
			<% else %>
				<a class="ajax" href="/unbounce">Un-Bounce</a>
			<% end %>
			
		</li>
	<% } %>
</ul>
